<%#
# Select Enum Form Partial

This partial renders a selectable text attribute,
to be displayed on a resource's new/edit form page.

## Local variables:

- `f`:
  A Rails form generator, used to help create the appropriate input fields.
- `field`:
  An instance of [Administrate::Field::Select][1].
  A wrapper around the attribute pulled from the database.

[1]: http://www.rubydoc.info/gems/administrate/Administrate/Field/Select_enum_field.rb
%>

<div class="field-unit__label">
  <%= f.label field.attribute %>
</div>
<div class="field-unit__field">
  <%= f.select(field.attribute) do %>
    <%= options_for_select(field.associated_resource_options, field.selected_option) %>
  <% end %>
</div>

